author: itv.com
title: TRAVEL - ROADS: HAMPSHIRE J11/M27 multi-vehicle crash at Fareham | Meridian
text:
There is queueing traffic at J11 / M27 westbound after a crash involving multiple vehicles. The slip road and the exit to the slip road for Fareham and Gosport are closed.
Last updated Wed 2 Sep 2015 Travel Hampshire The M27 Fareham Hampshire & Isle of Wight
